{
  "id": "adv_event_2408_01_05_02",
  "title": "敵はやっぱり",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い歓声だ……もう、スリクスは落ち目なんかじゃない）\n（頂点を狙う、トップクラスのアイドルの一角だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What an amazing cheer… ⅢX isn't in decline anymore.）\n（They're part of the top-class idols aiming for the summit.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.833349234,
      "endTime": 10.2333533029,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6211.901911
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13900
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "お、この間のライブバトルの記事出てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the article about the recent live battle is out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.36668879,
      "endTime": 16.4111786982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "『元BIG4のⅢX対実力派のやさぐれポメラニアン』\n『アイドルファンも唸る対戦カードだが、結果は』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Former BIG4‚ ⅢX vs. The skilled‚ Rebellious Pomeranian\"\n\"A matchup that even idol fans groan about‚ but the result is\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6000221233,
      "endTime": 27.8563714961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふん……ふふん、私達のことべた褒めじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm hmm… hehe‚ they're praising us to the skies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.06668879,
      "endTime": 34.704129280800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "うわ。にやにや笑っちゃってさ、キモっ。kanaは\nまだ『元BIG4』呼ばわりされてんのに腹立つけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh. You're grinning like that‚ gross. kana is\nstill annoyed about being called \"former BIG4\" though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9000251751,
      "endTime": 44.5669408779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、ライブバトルで一回勝って、褒められただけで\n満足してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you satisfied just from winning one live battle\nand getting praised?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666918418,
      "endTime": 49.883721317900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ。まさか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah. no way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1000251751,
      "endTime": 52.1499571066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "腑抜けてはいないようで何よりよ\n――私達の目的はただ一つ、トップに立つことだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's good that you haven't gone soft.\n――Our goal is only one thing: reaching the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3333585085,
      "endTime": 59.8773041071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ倒さないといけない奴らはいるんだからね\n一度勝ったくらいで、浮かれてなんかいられないっつの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are still lots of guys we need to defeat.\nWe can't get carried away just from winning once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0666918418,
      "endTime": 67.4354674957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "残りのBIG4、それに……\n月スト、サニピ、トリエル、リズノワ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The remaining BIG4‚ and also…\nMoon Tempest‚ Sunny Peace‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333585085,
      "endTime": 74.64977582110001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "考えなければ\nあの子達を倒すために、私達には何が必要なのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to think about\nwhat we need to defeat those girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8333585085,
      "endTime": 81.600818664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、また会議といきましょうか？\n観てる奴全員、驚かせてやろうじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ shall we have another meeting?\nLet's surprise everyone who's watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8000251751,
      "endTime": 89.7599573116,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}